# AC9 doc-check log

## Tooling

- `doc-check` skill (`~/projects/darren-workflow/skills/doc-check/SKILL.md`) targets
  projects with a `docs/_meta/doc-graph.json` DAG and/or a `build_semantic_roadmap.py`
  script. Spore, IC, PM have `_meta/project.json` but no `doc-graph.json` / semantic
  roadmap build script; the skill cannot validate those repos end-to-end.
- Spore fallback: `scripts/validate_spec_dag.py` — validates `doc_id` conformance,
  `depends_on` connectivity, and governed-doc frontmatter integrity across the
